  "question": "We have established for the smoking and lung cancer illustrative example that $n=11, b=0.02284$, $s_{\\left.Y\\right|_X}=8.349$, and $s_X=378.451$. Let us calculate a $95 \\%$ confidence for slope parameter $\\beta$.",
